 232+ 81CA              ; --- Print string within a bounded box (word-wraps at word boundaries) ---
 233+ 81CA              ; HL = ASCIZ string. Box starts at current (pr_col, pr_row).
 234+ 81CA              ; Wraps at column (pr_col + box_width). box_width must be set first.
