 317+ 9062              ; ================================================================
 318+ 9062              ; 8-bit multiply high byte: A = (A * B) >> 8
 319+ 9062              ; For inputs 0-100, result is 0-39 — good for gauge range 0-32.
 320+ 9062              ; Inputs: A, B. Returns A. Clobbers HL, DE, B.
 321+ 9062              ; ================================================================
 322+ 9062              mul8_hi:
