 338+ 9072              ; ================================================================
 339+ 9072              ; Compute pattern: compares last 3 pupil readings for consistency.
 340+ 9072              ; STABLE = all within 5 of each other, ERRATIC = max diff > 15,
 341+ 9072              ; otherwise SHIFTING.
 342+ 9072              ; Stores result in pattern_flag (0/1/2).
 343+ 9072              ; ================================================================
